parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid battery can cause the vehicle to stall, shut off, or experience electrical system failures, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the engine warning light illuminates
the vehicle tries to restart but fails
the hybrid battery leaks fluids.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to experience sudden shutdowns, stalling, or warning light illuminations, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The electrical system fails without warning
the vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
warning lights illuminate
the vehicle tries to restart but fails.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the hybrid mode can cause the vehicle to shut off or stall, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle moves into hybrid mode and suddenly shuts off
the vehicle tries to restart but fails
the engine warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and shut down, which can lead to accidents, especially on busy highways.
symptoms: The vehicle powers down to 50% before the engine shuts down
the vehicle refuses to start
the key seems stuck inside making it hard to turn or remove
the stabilitrak and service hybrid system warnings come on along with the check engine light.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to only move in reverse, making it difficult to control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle only moves in reverse
the transmission needs replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to become stuck in the "on" position, making it difficult to turn off the engine and remove the key, which can lead to security concerns and potential theft.
symptoms: The ignition switch cannot be turned to the off position
the key cannot be removed
the car cannot be turned off
the issue occurs regardless of the set of keys used.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and experience a range of warning lights, including stability control and airbag warnings, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's electrical system suddenly pulls back
all warning lights on the dashboard illuminate
the steering system locks up
the vehicle stalls
and the airbag and stability control systems malfunction.
